schema:description: Gurdial Singh Bains (1902-?). Son of Natha Singh. Village: Nagal Kalan, Garhshanker, Hoshaipur, Punjab. Was in United States 1924-1934. Joined Gadar Party along with Dilip Singh Phalla. Courtesy of Punjabi American Heritage Society.
